c: 3
v: 176
t: "(Aey Paighambar) jo log aaj kufr ki raah mein badi daud dhoop kar rahey hain unki sargarmiyan tumhein azurda na karein(grieve you). Yeh Allah ka kuch bhi na bigaad sakenge. Allah ka irada yeh hai ke unke liye aakhirat mein koi hissa na rakkhey, aur bil aakhir unko sakht saza milne wali hai"